ORM:
waterline, the doc
Here: Part 1 model
1. define a model you will extend the waterline.Collection object and add in your own attributes
   and methods.

   Be default, an attribute named id will be automatically added to the model with auto-incrementing.
   Also it will be the primary key.

   Also each model will also get two timestamp attributes added by default, the createdAt and updatedAt.
